1\u0103ng k\u00fd khi tham gia Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:15px\">Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac trao gi\u1ea3i: Trong v\u00f2ng 45 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:25px\">7. Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:15px\">Ph\u00f2ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n Th\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ea1i D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Taco Vi\u1ec7t Nam &#8211; Hotline: 1900.63.69.36<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-13233\" width=\"430\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim-724x1024.jpg 724w, https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim-212x300.jpg 212w, https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim-768x1086.jpg 768w, https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim-600x848.jpg 600w, https:\/\/tocotocotea.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/tocotoco-sinh-nhat-8-tuoi-8-nam-gan-ket-trieu-trai-tim.jpg 1018w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>8 N\u0102M G\u1eaeN K\u1ebeT TRI\u1ec6U TR\u00c1I T